Class SequentialScheduler

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Swimmer

    public class SequentialScheduler
extends Scheduler
    SequentialScheduler handles multiple Action by finishing them one at time.
    Basically, the Scheduler takes the first Action in the list, make it progress with each call of Action.doStep(), and when it is finished, takes the second Action, and so on.
    Author:
    Armand BOUR, Antoine PETIT
